        q: `An isolated 4 mm polyp is found by colonoscopy in the sigmoid colon of a 50-year-old woman. The excised polyp histologically reveals well-differentiated glands without invasion of the stalk. Which of the following would distinguish whether the polyp represents hyperplasia of the colonic mucosa or a neoplastic adenoma?`,
